{"description":"昨今主流の Windows 環境では、MS-DOS アプリケーションを動作させることが難しくなってきています。 工夫すれば可能なのでしょうが、 一般的な利用者にはかなりハードルが高いといえます。\n今後の開発体制も勘案した結果、「何でもいいから、とにかく早急に MARS を Windows 化する」ことが必要との結論に至り、このたび「MARS for Windows 暫定版」をリリースしました。","license":{"identifier":"Freeware"},"bin":"marswin.exe","shortcuts":[["marswin.exe","MARS"]],"extract_dir":"MARSWin","post_install":["$DesktopPath = [Environment]::GetFolderPath('Desktop')","if (!(Test-Path \"$DesktopPath\\MARS.lnk\")) {","  Write-Output \"Creating desktop shortcut for MARS...\"","  $WshShell = New-Object -ComObject WScript.Shell","  $Shortcut = $WshShell.CreateShortcut(\"$DesktopPath\\MARS.lnk\")","  $Shortcut.TargetPath = \"$dir\\marswin.exe\"","  $Shortcut.WorkingDirectory = \"$dir\"","  $Shortcut.Save()","} else {","  Write-Output \"Desktop shortcut for MARS already exists. Skipping creation.\"","}"],"uninstaller":{"script":["$DesktopPath = [Environment]::GetFolderPath('Desktop')","if (Test-Path \"$DesktopPath\\MARS.lnk\") {","  Write-Output \"Removing desktop shortcut for MARS...\"","  Remove-Item \"$DesktopPath\\MARS.lnk\" -Force","} else {","  Write-Output \"No desktop shortcut for MARS found. Skipping removal.\"","}"]},"version":"0.36","url":"https://www.swa785.net/pub/mars/marsw036.zip","homepage":"https://www.swa785.net/pub/mars/#marswin","hash":"6b1d28d28abab243e12c4724f7cfa968edea89c52daa35b4639457aaefba84dc","from":"https://github.com/Rumia-Channel/rumia_scoop"}
